targets.expr:
(sum(rate(http_server_request_duration_seconds_count{app=~"[[app]]"}[$interval])) - sum(rate(http_server_errors_total{app=~"[[app]]"}[$interval]) OR on() vector(0))) / 
( 
    sum(rate(http_server_request_duration_seconds_count{app=~"[[app]]"}[$interval])) - 
    sum(rate(http_server_errors_total{app=~"[[app]]", sli_error_type="invalid_request"}[$interval]) OR on() vector(0))
)

(sum(rate(http_server_request_duration_seconds_count{app=~"[[app]]"}[$interval])) - sum(rate(http_server_errors_total{app=~"[[app]]"}[$interval]) OR on() vector(0))) / 
( 
    sum(rate(http_server_request_duration_seconds_count{app=~"[[app]]"}[$interval])) - 
    sum(rate(http_server_errors_total{app=~"[[app]]", sli_error_type="invalid_request"}[$interval]) OR on() vector(0)) -           sum(rate(http_server_errors_total{app=~"[[app]]", sli_error_type="external_dependency"}[$interval]) OR on() vector(0))
)

(sum(rate(http_server_request_duration_seconds_count{app=~"[[app]]"}[$interval])) - sum(rate(http_server_errors_total{app=~"[[app]]"}[$interval]) OR on() vector(0))) / 
( 
    sum(rate(http_server_request_duration_seconds_count{app=~"[[app]]"}[$interval])) - 
    sum(rate(http_server_errors_total{app=~"[[app]]", sli_error_type="invalid_request"}[$interval]) OR on() vector(0)) -       
    sum(rate(http_server_errors_total{app=~"[[app]]", sli_error_type="internal_dependency"}[$interval]) OR on() vector(0)) -
    sum(rate(http_server_errors_total{app=~"[[app]]", sli_error_type="external_dependency"}[$interval]) OR on() vector(0))
)
